summary "Parsing Expression Grammars For Lua",
source "https://github.com/ezdiy/lua-lpeg.git"
detail "LPeg is a new pattern-matching library for Lua, based on Parsing"
detail "Expression Grammars (PEGs). The nice thing about PEGs is that it"
detail "has a formal basis (instead of being an ad-hoc set of features)"
detail "allows an efficient and simple implementation, and does most things"
detail "we expect from a pattern-matching library (and more, as we can"
detail "define entire grammars)."
homepage "http://www.inf.puc-rio.br/~roberto/lpeg.html"
license = "MIT/X11"
